Visual Suggestions 5
Suggestions:
  1. Apply for the HIB Visa during months such as October, November and December since their denial rates are lower and continue to decrease every year. 
  2. Apply for Teacher jobs  since their denial rates are lower and decrease YOY. 
  3. Avoid making mistakes on the Visa application to reduce the chances for denials.
